♪Hingga bisa bersatu♪

18
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:42,940
=Waktu Berlalu dan Kau di Sini=

19
00:01:43,140 --> 00:01:43,780
=Episode 15=

20
00:01:43,780 --> 00:01:46,560
(Hati di Surga, Raga di Dunia,
Hidup Sulit Diprediksi)

21
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:55,639
Bicaralah.

22
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:57,519
Jadi,…

23
00:01:59,559 --> 00:02:04,160
Jadi, teman bermainku saat kecil,
Kak Cheng dan Kak Ying menikah.

24
00:02:05,279 --> 00:02:08,839
Kami sekeluarga berencana
ingin pulang ke Yuyang.

25
00:02:11,959 --> 00:02:13,720
I… Ibuku…

26
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:19,039
Ibuku merasa kita sudah menikah.

27
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:23,160
Teman-teman desa di Yuyang
sangat penasaran padamu.

28
00:02:24,039 --> 00:02:26,039
Jadi, ingin kau ikut pulang juga.

29
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,160
Aku tak mau.

30
00:02:28,039 --> 00:02:28,880
Kenapa tak mau?

31
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:30,279
Kenapa aku harus mau?

32
00:02:31,679 --> 00:02:32,199
Karena…

33
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:36,160
Kudengar belakangan ini
suasana hatimu tak terlalu bagus.

34
00:02:36,679 --> 00:02:39,000
Bagaimana jika sekalian
melepas penat?

35
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,800
Melepas penat?

36
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:43,160
Desa kalian kotor dan berantakan.

37
00:02:43,559 --> 00:02:44,679
Apa aku bisa melepas penat?

38
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,180
Apa mau aku membuatmu
pulang dengan terhormat?

39
00:02:47,880 --> 00:02:48,800
Zhao Xiaoqian.

40
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:49,520
Aku kenapa?

41
00:02:51,119 --> 00:02:51,600
Baik.

42
00:02:52,679 --> 00:02:53,479
Aku mengerti.

43
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:54,920
Terserah kau mau pergi tidak.

44
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:57,260
Sekarang, aku akan pulang
dan bilang pada ibuku.

45
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,039
Sudah, 'kan?

46
00:03:10,330 --> 00:03:11,420
Kalian sebenarnya kenapa?

47
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,440
Apanya yang kenapa?

48
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:19,399
Tentu karena aku
mempermalukan keluargaku.

49
00:03:19,399 --> 00:03:20,440
Aku hanya menggerutu.

50
00:03:21,919 --> 00:03:24,080
Kenapa malu?
Apa yang sebenarnya terjadi?

51
00:03:26,679 --> 00:03:29,120
Kau tahu apa tulisan pada lentera
bunga yang dia bawa pulang?

52
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:32,839
"Ingin akhiri hubungan selamanya".

53
00:03:33,839 --> 00:03:34,880
Ini keinginan Xiaoman?

54
00:03:35,399 --> 00:03:36,919
Siapa lagi kalau bukan dia?

55
00:03:37,420 --> 00:03:39,850
Sekarang minta aku ikut mereka
hadiri pernikahan di Yuyang.

56
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:42,960
Mereka sekeluarga sungguh
tak menganggapku orang luar.

57
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,639
Jadi, apa kau sudah tanya padanya?

58
00:03:45,639 --> 00:03:47,119
Apa mungkin ada salah paham?

59
00:03:47,620 --> 00:03:49,930
- Xiaoman tak terlihat seperti…
- Kenapa jika terlihat beda?

60
00:03:50,300 --> 00:03:52,830
Dia mau akhiri hubungan denganku.
Aku harus tetap menyukainya?

61
00:03:52,830 --> 00:03:54,080
Jika benar salah paham,…

62
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:56,600
…kau jangan menambah
kesalahan lagi.

63
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,570
Aku main catur dulu.

64
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:07,039
Hanya menghadiri pernikahan saja.

65
00:04:07,279 --> 00:04:08,700
Dibujuk berkali-kali
tetap tak mau.

66
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:10,639
- Malah bilang pernikahan di desa…
- Maoya!

67
00:04:11,479 --> 00:04:12,119
Maoya.

68
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:13,880
Lihat.

69
00:04:15,320 --> 00:04:15,919
Lihat.

70
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:16,759
Ayam jantan.

71
00:04:17,720 --> 00:04:19,080
Untuk menambah nutrisi Pangeran.

72
00:04:23,860 --> 00:04:26,060
(Kediaman Pangeran)

73
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:27,980
Bunga harus dipotong dengan baik.

74
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:29,359
Hong Su, bereskan semuanya.

75
00:04:29,359 --> 00:04:29,839
Baik.

76
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,440
Kenapa ada ayam di kediaman?

77
00:04:35,320 --> 00:04:36,079
Nona Xie.

78
00:04:40,200 --> 00:04:41,359
Kau sungguh mencari masalah!

79
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:43,990
Beberapa hari lagi peringatan
kematian Adipati Yong.

80
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:46,279
Seluruh orang kediaman
sedang serius menyiapkannya.

81
00:04:46,550 --> 00:04:48,450
Kenapa hanya kau yang
selalu mencari masalah?

82
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:50,440
Bahkan berani bawa
hewan kotor ini ke kediaman.

83
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,640
Peringatan kematian Adipati Yong?

84
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:54,519
Cepat.

85
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:56,320
Cepat buang hewan kotor ini!

86
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:01,359
Pangeran!

87
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:02,959
Pangeran!

88
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,600
Kenapa berteriak?
Tak lihat aku sedang membaca?

89
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,320
Bibi Zhu mempersulit Nona Xie lagi.

90
00:05:08,799 --> 00:05:11,119
Hanya karena Nona Xie
membawa seekor ayam.

91
00:05:11,320 --> 00:05:11,920
Ayam?

92
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:14,660
Bibi adalah pengurus kediaman.
Apa salahnya mengatur dia?

93
00:05:15,279 --> 00:05:18,519
Jangan karena salah paham ini,
hatinya malah jadi merasa sedih.

94
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,640
Aku tak suka
mendengar perkataanmu.

95
00:05:24,359 --> 00:05:25,399
Apa aku tak sedih?

96
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,600
Apa aku tak punya hati?

97
00:05:27,100 --> 00:05:28,600
Kau juga tak tanya
dengan jelas dulu.

98
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:45,239
Nona Xie melanggar aturan.

99
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:48,239
Membawa hewan kotor ini
ke kediaman sesukanya.

100
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:51,280
Menurut aturan,
harus dihukum berat.

101
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:52,239
Bibi Zhu!

102
00:06:03,839 --> 00:06:04,600
Pangeran.

103
00:06:05,119 --> 00:06:09,839
Nona Xie berani membawa
hewan kotor ini ke dalam kediaman.

104
00:06:11,119 --> 00:06:15,200
Aku takut ini akan mengganggu
peringatan kematian Adipati Yong.

105
00:06:17,239 --> 00:06:19,839
Ibuku mendapatkannya
dari Kuil Konfusius.

106
00:06:19,839 --> 00:06:22,359
Katanya ingin aku memasakkan
sup untukmu dan Xingzhou…

107
00:06:22,359 --> 00:06:23,959
…sebagai penambah nutrisi, lalu…

108
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:27,380
…sebagai doa lulus ujian istana.

109
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,279
Sudahlah.

110
00:06:29,839 --> 00:06:32,079
Aku mengerti. Kugantikan
Bibi menghukumnya.

111
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,200
Nanti, akan kumasak kau.

112
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:49,760
Berhenti.

113
00:06:59,040 --> 00:07:00,079
Aku ingin tanya padamu.

114
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:12,640
Tadi, kau ingin tanya apa padaku?

115
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,359
Siapa namanya?

116
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:15,720
Siapa?

117
00:07:16,119 --> 00:07:16,640
Ayam.

118
00:07:18,359 --> 00:07:20,119
Keluargamu juga
memberi nama untuk ayam?

119
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,559
Kau sebenarnya ingin tanya apa?

120
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,000
Hanya tanya nama saja?

121
00:07:26,119 --> 00:07:27,040
Jangan cerewet.

122
00:07:28,119 --> 00:07:30,720
Ke depannya, panggil saja
Zhao Shengwu.

123
00:07:31,100 --> 00:07:33,080
Dulu, di rumah kami ada kuda
bernama Shengwu juga.

124
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:35,119
Itu kuda, ini ayam.

125
00:07:35,679 --> 00:07:37,839
Seekor ayam saja
kau beri margamu juga.

126
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:38,880
Kenapa kalau ayam?

127
00:07:38,880 --> 00:07:40,079
Apa ayam tak boleh punya nama?

128
00:07:40,510 --> 00:07:41,920
Selain itu, ini ayam Xingzhou, 'kan?

129
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:44,320
Xingzhou itu teman belajarku,
tentu ayam ini teman ayamku.

130
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,580
Tentu harus mengikuti margaku.

131
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:53,079
Kau sebenarnya ada masalah apa?

132
00:07:59,320 --> 00:08:00,040
Lentera bunga itu…

133
00:08:01,640 --> 00:08:02,680
Lentera bunganya kenapa?

134
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:07,120
Apa ibumu sungguh ingin
aku pergi ke Yuyang?

135
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:15,480
Kenapa belakangan ini kau aneh?

136
00:08:16,320 --> 00:08:17,559
Temperamenmu tak menentu.

137
00:08:18,519 --> 00:08:19,839
Aku sampai agak takut padamu.

138
00:08:22,359 --> 00:08:23,519
Apakah karena…

139
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,480
…masalah Adipati Yong?

140
00:08:27,679 --> 00:08:30,320
Jika suasana hatimu buruk,
tak apa-apa, boleh tak pergi.

141
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:31,320
Aku dan ibuku…

142
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:32,440
Kau berisik sekali.

143
00:08:37,380 --> 00:08:42,420
(Taman Ou)

144
00:08:44,719 --> 00:08:45,239
Sudahlah.

145
00:08:46,359 --> 00:08:46,919
Aku pergi.

146
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:50,119
Aku akan tanya
setelah kita pulang.

147
00:08:59,239 --> 00:09:00,559
Lihat ayamnya, jangan lihat aku.

148
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,559
Zhao Shengwu, ayo.

149
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:11,000
Paman Ji.

150
00:09:11,640 --> 00:09:14,679
Setiap hari, setelah layani Pangeran,
aku masih harus melayani kuda.

151
00:09:15,119 --> 00:09:16,650
Sekarang bertambah
seekor ayam lagi.

152
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,159
Kehidupan kita
sungguh menyedihkan.

153
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:21,599
Sayang sekali.

154
00:09:22,719 --> 00:09:24,180
Lihatlah betapa gemuknya ayam ini.

155
00:09:31,359 --> 00:09:33,880
Gigit!

156
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:37,799
Gigit sisi sebelahnya!

157
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:40,640
- Gigit!
- Gigit!

158
00:09:40,799 --> 00:09:41,239
Gigit!

159
00:09:41,239 --> 00:09:42,239
Gigit.

160
00:09:42,479 --> 00:09:44,119
Bagus!

161
00:09:46,359 --> 00:09:47,119
Berikan uangmu.

162
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,559
Ayo, Yan Bawang.

163
00:09:58,479 --> 00:10:02,280
Kudengar Xu Shu dari sekolah pemerintah
mengadakan Acara Adu Jangkrik.

164
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:05,640
Semua bangsawan di akademi
mendapatkan undangan.

165
00:10:06,239 --> 00:10:08,080
A… Acara Adu Jangkrik?

166
00:10:08,359 --> 00:10:09,400
Apa kau tak dapat?

167
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,840
Tak mungkin.

168
00:10:11,300 --> 00:10:13,380
Bagaimanapun, kau putra
dari Kepala Administrasi.

169
00:10:13,479 --> 00:10:14,440
Tak mungkin.

170
00:10:15,719 --> 00:10:16,479
Tak aneh juga.

171
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:18,270
Putra Kepala Administrasi…

172
00:10:19,239 --> 00:10:21,719
…selalu mengikuti Pangeran
sebagai bawahannya.

173
00:10:21,719 --> 00:10:22,479
Apa namanya ini?

174
00:10:22,760 --> 00:10:25,799
Ini namanya diberi status tinggi,
malah mau menjadi bawahan.

175
00:10:26,479 --> 00:10:28,840
Lama kelamaan, tentu akan
diremehkan orang lain.

176
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:30,640
Kau sedang omong kosong apa?

177
00:10:32,119 --> 00:10:34,039
Besok, aku akan bawa
Zhao Xiaoqian ke sana.

178
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:37,840
Kuperlihatkan pada kalian
apa itu saudara yang sesungguhnya.

179
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,320
Siapkanlah uangmu.

180
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:43,200
Nanti, aku akan memenangkan
seluruh uangmu.

181
00:10:44,640 --> 00:10:47,440
Ayo pergi, Yan Bawang!

182
00:11:32,239 --> 00:11:32,799
Ibu.

183
00:11:33,640 --> 00:11:35,180
Untuk apa kau membawa
ayam dan bebek?

184
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,479
Di Yuyang juga ada.

185
00:11:36,479 --> 00:11:37,039
Tak apa-apa.

186
00:11:38,559 --> 00:11:39,239
Aku bisa.

187
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:47,180
(Yuyang)

188
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,440
- Sudah datang.
- Sudah datang.

189
00:11:50,479 --> 00:11:51,200
Nona Xie!

190
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,359
- Sudah datang.
- Nona Xie!

191
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:57,679
Sudah sampai.

192
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:03,440
Kakak Ipar Liu.

193
00:12:08,359 --> 00:12:09,440
Nona Xie.

194
00:12:12,119 --> 00:12:13,359
- Halo, Kepala Desa.
- Halo.

195
00:12:15,719 --> 00:12:16,960
Akhirnya, sudah sampai!

196
00:12:17,359 --> 00:12:18,119
Apa kabarmu baik?

197
00:12:18,119 --> 00:12:19,239
Baik.

198
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:19,960
Baguslah.

199
00:12:21,559 --> 00:12:22,119
Baiklah.

200
00:12:22,119 --> 00:12:23,239
Pasangan rupawan.

201
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:28,440
Pangeran datang kemari,
sambutan kami masih kurang layak.

202
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:29,980
Kepala Desa, berdirilah.

203
00:12:30,479 --> 00:12:32,760
Hari ini aku datang sebagai
menantu di Yuyang.

204
00:12:33,010 --> 00:12:34,280
Kalian tak perlu terlalu sopan.

205
00:12:35,239 --> 00:12:36,200
Baik.

206
00:12:36,200 --> 00:12:38,559
Maoya sungguh menikah
dengan pria hebat.

207
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:42,400
Jika dilihat, pria dari kota
memang berbeda.

208
00:12:42,599 --> 00:12:43,159
Kepala Desa!

209
00:12:44,239 --> 00:12:44,760
Kepala Desa!

210
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:46,799
Acara segera dimulai,
ayo kita pergi ke halaman.

211
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:47,479
Baik.

212
00:12:47,479 --> 00:12:48,200
Sudah mulai.

213
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:48,880
Pangeran.

214
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,159
Silakan.

215
00:12:50,559 --> 00:12:51,119
Ayo jalan.

216
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:52,640
Pangeran, silakan.

217
00:12:58,599 --> 00:12:59,960
Aku senang melihatnya.

218
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:01,239
- Lihatlah hasilnya.
- Mari.

219
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:03,320
Pangeran, makan.

220
00:13:03,559 --> 00:13:04,840
- Terima kasih.
- Makan yang banyak.

221
00:13:06,239 --> 00:13:07,010
- Mari.
- Terima kasih.

222
00:13:07,010 --> 00:13:08,919
Tak ada makanan enak di desa.

223
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,039
Pangeran.

224
00:13:13,640 --> 00:13:14,679
Ayam dari desa.

225
00:13:16,919 --> 00:13:18,159
Terima kasih.

226
00:13:18,320 --> 00:13:19,039
Makan.

227
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:24,200
Dia datang untuk bersulang.

228
00:13:25,440 --> 00:13:26,640
Da Cheng ingin bersulang?

229
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:33,119
Pangeran kami paling perhatian
pada Xiaoman.

230
00:13:33,520 --> 00:13:35,039
Minum arak pasti tak masalah, 'kan?

231
00:13:36,280 --> 00:13:38,119
Bersulanglah, kenapa diam saja?

232
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:40,530
Bersulang lebih awal,
bisa lebih cepat punya anak.

233
00:13:40,530 --> 00:13:42,520
Dia pejabat yang datang dari kota.

234
00:13:42,799 --> 00:13:45,080
Mana terbiasa minum
arak biasa kita?

235
00:13:45,599 --> 00:13:46,039
Benar, 'kan?

236
00:13:46,039 --> 00:13:47,080
Tak apa-apa, mari.

237
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:48,810
